name: Gochuumon wa Usagi Desu ka?? Wonderful party!

description:
Gochuumon wa Usagi Desu ka?? Wonderful party! is an adventure game developed by 5pb. It came out on 03-03-2016. It was published by 5pb Games.
You can play Gochuumon wa Usagi Desu ka?? Wonderful party! on PS Vita.
